Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:11.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 對方的要求是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.77,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「未支付的報酬 外加50%的滯納金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共計750萬美元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:22.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以現金或是金塊的形式 在今天之內交付」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先不說金額 給的時間也太少了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:30.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也許他們從一開始就沒有想交涉的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:34.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是說他們只是為了殺雞儆猴 就會殺了那個男的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.34,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就為了區區750萬美元？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}並非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估計他們並不知道人質的真實身分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說到底為什麼會淪落到這種局面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:54.10,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是一開始就遵守和他們的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會演變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:01.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柳井董事 現在可不是清點責任的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:07.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目前 如何解決這一事態是更優先的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道束手無策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:16.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們公司不能失去他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:46.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早 伊莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又刷新了這條路線的記錄？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:59.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這倒是挺厲害 不過安全系統發動的次數太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這可是公路 駕駛時多小心一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係 入學至今沒出過事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:18.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話說回來 今天來我們班的轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽說是個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:20.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:22.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這反應太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這可是邂逅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一個小小的大事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.90,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是小還是大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你還是提不起興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然轉入了我們班 那肯定是個怪咖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:42.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別連著自己一起抹黑好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:57.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對方擅自設下的時限根本毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但這樣的話人質就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有這個辦法了 柳井董事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:21.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您可知道世界上有多少霧科的挖掘場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但現在被抓住的可是你們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論是誰都不能區別對待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總裁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:29.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.91,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛剛討論的一事現在還不算是案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是業務上的小麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還請各位千萬不要向外走漏風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.29,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瀨良老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.90,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 校長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保安部和工會也會衝我發火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.15,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過這點怨言也就限於今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快要完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:29.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:34.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}SWNPR方程式用試作2號機 X-2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}裝載了比X-1提高了5%的動力和比衝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改良型SWNPR引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.00,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最高時速25萬公里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有了它 下一期的競速中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們就能創下史無前例的賽道記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:53.15,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真希望能在我任職期間看它飛上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:57.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十分抱歉 目前還無法確保其安全性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}考慮到測試飛行員身上的負擔 這也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實我是最想駕駛它的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.39,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還對當飛行員戀戀不捨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.76,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我毫不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我現在有了新的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.76,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}新的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}培養未來的工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:35.00,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一起在宇宙航天產業裡掀起新的革新 這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.53,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這也是校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 是笹山部長您的話鼓勵了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喔？我說過那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您說「人本身就是寶物」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「培育人才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是建起支撐企業 社會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乃至世界的擎天巨柱」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一想到從A-TEC中會走出第二第三個瀨良海斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:09.10,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不 我和他們就沒差幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}實打實的現役選手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了 該開晨會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好 我是笹山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.55,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事 現在我有空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼他現在抵達了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各…各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話說我們的特別節目是在今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:47.55,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是好好宣傳了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:51.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看到我們造出的機器 肯定都要嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真想快點進行試飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.54,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位 你們這樣由奈很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.10,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好聽她說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老師也說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎？啊…這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}關於預算這件事 我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次班會上再認真討論下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:17.77,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼晨會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個最會浪費的行家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡可能真是怪咖班…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.95,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了 海斗親 還有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在教室裡要叫我老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:39.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別說這個了 那個要來的轉學生怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.15,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.29,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他好像遲到了 所以還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我記得他是木衛三來的歸國子女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是出境時出了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 你說的我還第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼連這都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該說是我們只知道這點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要接觸轉學生的人事訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但安全等級太高 我是徹底束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過是個轉學生 這也太不尋常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在我們班這裡也要特殊對待他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別刨根問底了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作吾 洩露機密可會受懲戒處分的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算了吧老師 這只是安全檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我每次找到安全漏洞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不都會連對策都加上 提交報告的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是說這個 而是說你們的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你聽好 同學們也聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:39.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們的確是霧科公司選拔出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}換句話說就是菁英生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:45.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過不要進了這個班就自恃甚高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為你們在身為這A-TEC的一員之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:55.54,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先是霧科學園 乃至霧科集團的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然你們是我的學生 就給我扔掉菁英觀念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要把同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:01.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把職員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把在這霧科工作的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全都當做家人來對待！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又開始嘮叨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當自己昭和年代的工薪族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我哥哥這話匣子一開就停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來 跟我複述
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「謙虛 誠實 正直」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 就這樣談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們現在正與你所屬的公司做交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然對你多有不便 還請再忍耐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.62,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們會保證你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:45.53,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過只有你們公司老實答應交易才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}轉學生被抓了當人質？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道Coldwood嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.95,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是那顆資源型小行星？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:59.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 霧科在那邊出資建有氦-3挖掘場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:05.77,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但公司與那邊的工作人員在酬勞上起了爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把他給捲入了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但他為什麼會在那麼危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:13.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他父母是和霧科有關係的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對方要求獲得當初定下的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果拿不到錢就滅口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那趕緊把錢付了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說到底都怪霧科欠薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多虧柳井副總裁的決定 支付上有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是事情沒有這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個挖掘場決定要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}銀行也撤離了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且他們連戶頭都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一群按天算錢的僱工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那該怎麼付錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽說他們的條件是要求以現金或金塊的方式送到當地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且今天之內就要送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太荒唐了 只剩8個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以一般的航線…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 等一下 我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這樣 瀨良老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不要告訴學生這件事 就交給你定奪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.34,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但請不要因此而太過不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能趕上！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:29.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走這條路線的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瀨良老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很遺憾 公司是不會滿足你們的要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}擺出這種態度可不是聰明人該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們的做法沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是選錯人質了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別慌 只是張名片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:04.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:09.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如你所見 我在那個公司裡的立場比較微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公司裡也有想把你們的提案連著我的存在一起抹消掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們最好小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.68,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是要恐嚇我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我是在和你們談生意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不來一起考慮一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們全員都能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}並且都能獲益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雙贏的解決方案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這樣 為了救出轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.46,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必須在今天之內將現金送至當地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:42.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天之內…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到Coldwood緊趕慢趕至少也要13小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒戲唱 這絕對沒戲唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對 應該是沒戲唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}…對於我們以外的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼意思 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後把轉學生帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用上X-2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說什麼呢 海斗親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}連試飛都還沒做過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是你自己說還得花兩週調整的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:22.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且老師到目前為止一次都沒飛過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:25.76,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧 我以前還參加過競速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:26.73,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有國際B級執照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是多少年前的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}偶爾相信下老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除了我們的X-2外就別無他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們一起去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:42.89,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為哥哥你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像這樣 到Coldwood的路線繞了一個大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想在今天內到達是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.53,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我們走這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}距離約為原始線路的三分之二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}靠我們這台機器 能在今天內到達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.77,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個 您畫出的這條路線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.68,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像若無其事地經過了禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:23.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個…所以說 有我們A-TEC優秀的機組人員支援的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一兩個禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.29,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒戲唱！絕對沒戲唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是我們的皇牌也沒戲唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我 瀨良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡是管制室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您這讓我很困擾啊 瀨良室長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊？什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.00,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}起飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿你沒轍 今天幫你搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次麻煩在兩天前申請啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:07.91,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 所以你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每次都太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:28.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說回來 我們真的有執行解救人質作戰的權限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這明顯是牽扯全公司的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上頭還沒動靜 我們擅自行動果然還是不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:37.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起這些 現在最不妙的是伊莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道是哪個神經大條的哥哥搞出來的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起 我完全沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能聽到嗎 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去救轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.10,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要去的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才是正規機師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能交給外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別想著要維護我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.68,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒這樣想過 完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唔…你這麼乾脆地否定還是有點小受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 美月在擔心老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.39,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊 伊莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快停下 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}預定路線上的禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是小行星帶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼不早說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啟動系統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}All systems go！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}影像來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}X-2 請你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒問題 通過密集地帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情況怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}左側輔助推進器裝甲破損
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目前對航行不構成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.39,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個推進器的裝甲零件是特別訂製的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}破損部位出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.39,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現將推進器分離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知不知道這個推進器有多貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是 老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別管了 動手吧 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.89,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全第一 任務第二 沒有三四 代價第五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:48.91,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:57.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}8億塊的推進器…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}確認到Coldwood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:16.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}預計到達時間 2355
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趕上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們做的引擎果然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.76,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}畢竟得了海斗老師直傳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.68,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}X-2 請報告損壞情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}預備燃料罐嚴重損毀 已經分離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.13,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷卻器部分破損
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.62,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:50.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}2億5千萬…3億…6億8千萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幹的好 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後就是進入屋子運輸升降口 交付錢款
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:58.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽好了 千萬不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先給他們看錢 表現你沒有無抵抗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:07.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了 能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:10.50,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}著陸系統不工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作吾 知道原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:17.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只知道修復需要不少時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明早之前肯定可以修好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白崎 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在我們這邊在著手修復系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧 肯定能修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:41.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先暫且繞Coldwood環行 等待下一個指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂等一下 白崎 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:47.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不是沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:54.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是打算衝進去吧 是這樣對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以這機體的狀況 不可能衝得進去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.91,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是轉學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}綁架犯們在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼沒人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:01.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才要問你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:12.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在人類仍然對宇宙心懷憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}充滿開拓者精神的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.15,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太陽系各行星都被「地球化」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無數人們在其上安居樂業
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:40.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火星便是其中的一個行星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:44.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上面散布著各個國家的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:47.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個故事便是以在其上築建起的日本新的都道府縣之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「第四東京都」為舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:56.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}年輕的高中上班族們所描繪出的青春塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是這個A-TEC的領隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個嘛…我是班導師瀨良
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:13.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 是你昨天指揮的解救人質行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:17.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我 那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是糟糕至極的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這地方比傳聞裡說的還累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也明白為什麼老哥要嘆氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我等一下 你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們浪費了太多資金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:33.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}資 資金？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本次解救行動的支出為5億
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:43.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加上行動之後的機械和系統維護費
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:45.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還要追加5億左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:49.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但這都只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:55.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次嚴重損毀的試作機的開發費用 總額為150億
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以為這是贖金的多少倍？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:07.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在說存在對我見死不救這個選項
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:11.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 在那情況下這才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:16.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:21.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近幾年來你們A-TEC每年的預算超過500億
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:26.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從我們公司的規模來說也是不能忽略的數字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:29.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.50,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧科公司 先進技術開發部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧羽渚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:47.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}轉學生是…我們的上司？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:49.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}霧羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道你是社長的同族？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:58.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我身上的任務是將你們A-TEC解體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:01.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是裁了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:10.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:12.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從今開始請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:17.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:21.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最多只能再留這組織一年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:22.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然是來真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吐槽就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:26.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎呀 真是太棒了 瀨良老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.01,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.23,0:24:29.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這下頭痛了
